title: Giant Hidroacanthoma Simplex Mimicking Bowen's Disease.
label: Fig. 1
caption: A 70 × 50 mm, well-circumscribed, dark reddish-brown, elevated plaque on the right flank part.

title: Giant Hidroacanthoma Simplex Mimicking Bowen's Disease.
label: Fig. 2
caption: A Low-power view showing well-circumscribed intraepidermal nests within an acanthotic epidermis (HE stain. Original magnification ×40). B High-power view showing small and relatively monomorphic tumor cells with no atypia (HE. ×100). C Diffuse lumican staining was noted (×40).
